title: Deal: VRS Design Cases for LG V20, Google Pixel Starting at $4.99 – 2/7/17
text:
Deal: VRS Design Cases for LG V20, Google Pixel Starting at $4.99 – 2/7/17   Alexander Maxham 
Those that are looking to pick up a new case for their Google Pixel, Pixel XL or LG V20, well you’re in luck. VRS Design is offering up some of their best cases over on eBay for some pretty incredible prices. The Crystal Bumper, High Pro Shield and Simpli Mod for the Pixel and Pixel XL are available for $4.99 each in multiple colors. For the LG V20, the Crystal Bumper and High Pro Shield are available for $4.99 with the Layered Dandy coming in at $8.99. Pretty great prices for some pretty incredible looking cases. 
Now the way that this works is that you’ll need to click on the button below, from there you’ll see all of the VRS Design cases that are on sale. Just simply choose the case you want for the device you want and add it to your cart. You won’t see the discounted price until it is in your cart. So if you see it stating that it’s $15.99, don’t worry about it, add the case to your cart and you’ll be good to go. This is one of those sales that you definitely won’t want to miss out on. It’s unclear how long it’ll be available, so you’ll want to take advantage of it.
